    <item>
      <title>基尔·斯塔默将访问乌克兰，讨论战后维和部队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/keir-starmer-to-visit-ukraine-to-discuss-postwar-peacekeeping-force</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默将在未来几周前往乌克兰，讨论在与俄罗斯的冲突结束后在乌克兰部署国际维和部队的可能性，这是他半年前担任英国首相以来首次访问这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/keir-starmer-to-visit-ukraine-to-discuss-postwar-peacekeeping-force</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 12:55:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派抓住希望，马杜罗巩固权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/maduro-cements-power-in-venezuela-as-opposition-grasps-for-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在竞争对手四散而去、举步维艰的情况下，委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗宣誓就任第三个六年总统，无视国际社会对其虚假选举和残酷镇压异见的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/maduro-cements-power-in-venezuela-as-opposition-grasps-for-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 12:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国市场动荡后，里夫斯力图深化与中国的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/reeves-bids-to-deepen-china-ties-after-week-of-uk-market-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周末，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯将成为七年来访问北京的最高级英国官员，在英国市场动荡有可能破坏其刺激国内增长计划的背景下，她将着手深化与中国的经济联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/reeves-bids-to-deepen-china-ties-after-week-of-uk-market-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
